  <span class="py-0 px-1 text-sm uppercase" style="background-color:#edf2f7;">Poster</span>
  <span class="font-medium">Interphase Human Chromosome Exhibits Out Of Equilibrium Glassy Dynamics</span>
  <span class="italic">CSHL Single Biomolecules, 2018</span>
  </li>
  <li>
  <span class="py-0 px-1 text-sm uppercase" style="background-color:#edf2f7;">Poster</span>
  <span class="font-medium">Glass-like dynamics in the folded state of human interphase chromosome</span>
  <span class="italic">APS March Meeting, 2017</span>
  </li>
</ol>
</section>
